ONE daemon boot, SP_B3_DISPOSER=2, NO SP_B3_SECRET (each episode self-ablates with its
own ep.secret sidecar). ONE /v1/chat request (auto_recall=true) -> the disposer iterates
all 21 episodes: inject E -> teacher-force E's own secret -> ablate E's source rows
(cudaMemset) -> re-score -> collapse = SigmaDeltaLL over the secret window -> O(1) rewind.
Admission rule: ACCEPT iff collapse < TAU=-8.0 (the v13 pin); parametric control ~0 = REJECT.

